          "type": "game",
          "x": 0,
          "y": -72,
          "width": 184,
          "height": 318,
          "title": "Oswald’s Diary",
          "tagline": "Uncover the truth behind New Orleans’ most infamous visitor.",
          "guideName": "Jack Martin",
          "price": "Free to Start / $14.99 in game purchase",
          "builderNotes": "",
          "tags": [
            "Conspiracy",
            "Mystery"
          ],
          "body": "On August 9th, 1963, a well traveled 23-year-old man was arrested in New Orleans for disturbing the peace.\n\n3 months later he was arrested in Dallas, and immediately became the presumptive assassin of President John F. Kennedy.\n\n2 days later he too was fatally shot.\n\nThat young man was Lee Oswald.\n\nThose are facts.\n\nFrom here on out, anything you discover may be fact, or it may be fiction.\n\nThat’s for you to decipher.\n\nYou’ve found Oswald’s Diary.\n\nYour mission is to take it to the city where he was born and get it into the right hands before it’s too late.",
          "varName": "",
          "acceptAny": false,
          "anytime": false,
          "anytimePairId": "",
          "rotation": 0,
          "orderIndex": 100
        }
      ],
      "links": []
