          "builderNotes": "",
          "tags": [],
          "body": "Despite the painful memories that seem to surface whenever Minnesota and New Orleans meet, one thing is undeniable: New Orleans is a great away game destination. And beyond the bars and t-shirt shops of Bourbon Street, there’s an even better way to experience it. Set just outside the famed French Quarter, this immersive game combines the fun of a scavenger hunt with the challenge of an escape room. Created by a New Orleans native, this \"Takeover Game\" just might be the best part of your trip, especially if your team loses.",
